    <name>The High Stile Ridge from Gatescarth, Buttermere</name>
    <bounds minlat="54.5078834" minlon="-3.3131616" maxlat="54.5438521" maxlon="-3.2547920" />
  </metadata>
  <rte>
    <name>The High Stile Ridge from Gatescarth, Buttermere</name>
    <desc>One of the Lake District's great ridge walks. From the shores of Buttermere the delights of the High Stile Ridge are not completely apparent as the shoulders of High Stile do limit the view of the ridge itself and this walk gradually uncovers the wonders of this lofty trio of mountains.</desc>
    <author>Copyright Walking Britain</author>
	<url>www.walkingbritain.co.uk/walk-1153-description</url>
	<urlname>Walk - The High Stile Ridge from Gatescarth, Buttermere</urlname>
      
